      "span_text": "Oscillatory behavior has also been observed for a non-mammalian axonemal dynein under loads applied using optical tweezers  ]; though in that study, the MT was interacting with 1-4 dynein arms whereas in our study even the shortest oscillating MT is likely associated with 10 times that many."
